  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you can generate a large amount of chakra at your feet and send yourself high into the air.</p><p> Roll 2 flurry die and multiply the result by 5.</p><p> The final result determines how high you travel in feet into the air.</p><p> While in the air, you can glide up to your movement speed, you treat the maximum range of ranged weapons as their normal range, and melee weapon attacks you make while falling within 5 feet of a creature have advantage.</p><p> You take no damage from falling.</p><p></p>",
